{"tid":2177230,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李宇軒年初專訪：「香港自由民主法治化為烏有」 劉偉聰:港人甘冒無限風險偷渡 反映對《國安法》侵害人權和法治的恐懼","createTime":"2020-08-27T14:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T18:15:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"88b264620463ef97d0ab0e9d8172fda65bc12711","tid":2177230,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:28:48.000Z","msg":"逃亡台灣失敗，正被廣東公安扣押的「香港故事」成員李宇軒，於今年初接受本台專訪時稱，不滿連番惡法和中共極權令香港原有的自由、民主和法治化為烏有，冀全球各地港人連成一線盡其全力「救港」。有香港大律師嘆言，港人竟甘冒無限風險偷渡，反映對《國安法》的恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n今年4月中旬，李宇軒以「攬炒團隊」發言人身分接受本台專訪，講述該組織在「反送中」運動中發揮國際戰線的角色。他表示，該組織冀凝聚世界各地香港人開展政治遊說，以一個沒有大台的方式運作，推動香港民主運動。他又形容去年「G20」峰會期間的行動引起國際社會關注，是「重要的里程碑」。<br />\n<br />\n過去經常為社運人士辯護的大律師劉偉聰指，這批偷渡人士將面對的風險是「難以估計」，尤其是在內地被捕，在檢控和法律過程中， 恐難以享受基本權利，加上沒有新聞自由，「這些人士會受甚麼對待，都不會被報道。」他嘆言港人竟甘冒無限風險偷渡，反映對《國安法》侵害人權和法治的恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李宇軒今次偷渡被捕的消息傳出後，引起社會廣泛關注，本台記者曾多次嘗試聯絡他本人，但他的手機一直無法接通。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-lee-08272020064607.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-lee-08272020064607.html&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONgQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=4b4ba59c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-lee-08272020064607.html</a>"},{"pid":"6347caa3644a63fcbceb6bb3ed2fdda2beff2951","tid":2177230,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1678fc048834ffd74d445db9fbb511d181c51f3","tid":2177230,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6347caa3644a63fcbceb6bb3ed2fdda2beff2951","tid":2177230,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b19a826e047ce90b75209b52b76d3f498a0ba1d","tid":2177230,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:33:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cdf00ffe4435781dc473c2631b5a478f9e62b4","tid":2177230,"uid":305083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:34:44.000Z","msg":"已經肯定船果度既人有李宇軒份?"},{"pid":"e074a8cc077c929b00df04eda3a3af1097ab6a92","tid":2177230,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ee5b0bdce7ebff8f1b042847b6cac427cc6d15","tid":2177230,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2cdf00ffe4435781dc473c2631b5a478f9e62b4","tid":2177230,"uid":305083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:34:44.000Z","msg":"已經肯定船果度既人有李宇軒份?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:40:14.000Z","msg":"佢本人/認識佢嘅人冇任何一個出嚟報平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c